cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with object tracking and detection in videos, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a method for automated category discovery and detector learning, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of large-scale unlabeled videos also suggests a potential application in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
